snippet.title: Planetary Defense Duel gameplay
snippet.description: After a long hiatus of my game development, this is my first project which I made with the Godot engine over 5 weeks. It is a take on the arcade space shooter in which two players must try to destroy each other's ship. The game will soon be available for free on itch.io.
